quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  12,94,"Nígbà tí èrò-ràkúnmí náà sí pínyà (kúrò lọ́dọ̀ Ànábì Yūsuf), bàbá wọn sọ pé: “Dájúdájú èmi ń gbọ́ òórùn Yūsuf tí ẹ kò bá níí sọ pé mò ń jarán.”"
  12,95,"Wọ́n sọ pé: “A fi Allāhu búra! Dájúdájú ìwọ sì wà nínú àṣìṣe rẹ ti àtijọ́ (nípa ìfẹ́ Yūsuf).”"
  12,96,"Nígbà tí oníròó-ìdùnnú dé, ó ju (ẹ̀wù náà) lé e níwájú, ó sì ríran padà. Ó sọ pé: “Ǹjẹ́ èmi kò sọ fún yín pé dájúdájú mo mọ ohun tí ẹ kò mọ̀ nípa Allāhu.”"
  14,40,"Olúwa mi, ṣe èmi àti nínú àrọ́mọdọ́mọ mi ní olùkírun. Olúwa wa, kí O sì gba àdúà mi."
  14,41,"Olúwa mi, ṣàforíjìn fún èmi àti àwọn òbí mi méjèèjì àti àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo ní ọjọ́ tí ìṣírò-iṣẹ́ yóò ṣẹlẹ̀.”"
  14,42,"Má ṣe lérò pé Allāhu gbàgbé n̄ǹkan tí àwọn alábòsí ń ṣe níṣẹ́. Ó kàn ń lọ́ wọn lára dí ọjọ́ kan tí àwọn ojú yóò yọ síta ràngàndàn."
  15,13,"Wọn kò níí gbà á gbọ́; ìṣe (Allāhulórí) àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́ kúkú ti ré kọjá. {1}",footnotes:1:Ìṣe Allāhu lórí ẹ̀dá lásìkò ìparun àwọn ìjọ ìṣáájú ni pé, Allāhu - subhānahu wa ta'ālā - gba àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo là, Ó sì pa àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ run gẹ́gẹ́ bí ó ṣe ṣẹlẹ̀ sí ìjọ Ànábì Nūh, ìjọ Ànábì Lūt àti bẹ́ẹ̀ bẹ́ẹ̀ lọ.
  15,14,"Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé A ṣí ìlẹ̀kùn kan sílẹ̀ fún wọn láti inú sánmọ̀, tí wọn kò sì yé gbabẹ̀ gùnkè lọ (sínú sánmọ̀),"
  15,15,"dájúdájú wọ́n á wí pé: “Wọ́n kan fi n̄ǹkan bo ojú wa ni. Rárá, ènìyàn tí wọ́n ń dan ni àwa sẹ́.”"